tyler is no more on the second channel. barely much remnants of the tech bro anymore.

the true test awaits. 👀

Ashley caught the bouquet. 😱

Love you babe. ❤️
i’m a tourist…on this planet. woah deep

congrats on getting married, G. ❤️ 
like a second older brother growing up!
finally got to meet roman! had an absolute blast on the podcast 🔥

Thankful for all of you guys. Thank you for still continuing to watch and support my family and I for nearly a decade now.

Won’t ever forget it. Juggies4Life ❤️
